  "text": "In the multiple antenna variant of this model, the channel coefficients c n, are R × T matrices, where R, resp. T , is the number of antennas at the receiver, resp. transmitter. In this case, the N × K matrices F n and G n given by Equation [CITATION_1] when L > 0 are block triangular matrices with N := RL and K := T L.",
